  "body": "---------------------------\r\n## Issue\r\n@truffle/contract depends on @truffle/debug-utils which depends on @trufflesuite/chromafi which depends on ansi-mark which is [vulnerable](https://github.com/F1LT3R/ansi-mark/issues/2), throws [warnings on every run](https://github.com/F1LT3R/ansi-mark/issues/3) (as does super-split, also a dependency of chromafi from the same developer), and isn't maintained.\r\n\r\nIt would be better if either:\r\nA. Trufflesuite forks and maintains ansi-mark, updates the reference from chromafi, and issues an update on chromafi, or \r\nB. Truffle/debug-utils finds a way to drop chromafi. ",
